### Week 10 — Spring MVC 패턴 전체 테스트 (swframework 실 엔드포인트 기준)
### IntelliJ HTTP Client: 각 요청 왼쪽 ▶ 버튼으로 개별 실행
### 본 프로젝트는 W07 LoginInterceptor 활성 — [Login]을 가장 먼저 실행해 세션 획득.
### 사전 조건:
###   H2 모드   : ./gradlew bootRun --args='--spring.profiles.active=h2'
###   MySQL 모드: ./gradlew bootRun --args='--spring.profiles.active=mysql'

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# [Login] 세션 획득 (LoginInterceptor 통과)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [Login] admin 계정으로 로그인 → JSESSIONID 쿠키 획득
# @no-redirect
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

loginId=admin&password=1234

> {%
client.test("로그인 후 redirect", () =>
    client.assert([302, 303].includes(response.status)));
%}

###

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Lab 01 — 학생 CRUD (W10 swframework 적용)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [Lab01-1] 목록 — DataInitializer가 초기 3건 INSERT
GET {{baseUrl}}/students
Accept: text/html

> {%
client.test("상태코드 200", () => client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("초기 3건 표시", () =>
    client.assert(response.body.includes("홍길동") &&
                  response.body.includes("김영희") &&
                  response.body.includes("이철수")));
%}

###

### [Lab01-2] 등록 폼
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/new

> {%
client.test("폼 페이지", () => client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("name input", () => client.assert(response.body.includes('name="name"')));
client.test("studentId input", () => client.assert(response.body.includes('name="studentId"')));
%}

###

### [Lab01-3] 정상 등록 → PRG (302 Redirect → /students/{id})
# @no-redirect
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=박지성&studentId=202300004&email=park@tukorea.ac.kr

> {%
client.test("Redirect 302/303", () =>
    client.assert([302, 303].includes(response.status)));
client.test("Location: /students/{id}", () =>
    client.assert(/\/students\/\d+$/.test(response.headers.valueOf("Location"))));
const m = response.headers.valueOf("Location").match(/\/students\/(\d+)$/);
if (m) client.global.set("newStudentId", m[1]);
%}

###

### [Lab01-4] 상세 조회 (방금 생성된 학생)
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/{{newStudentId}}

> {%
client.test("상세 200", () => client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("박지성 표시", () => client.assert(response.body.includes("박지성")));
%}

###

### [Lab01-5] 삭제 (직전 생성된 학생)
# @no-redirect
POST {{baseUrl}}/students/{{newStudentId}}/delete

> {%
client.test("삭제 후 redirect", () => client.assert([302, 303].includes(response.status)));
%}

###

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Lab 02 — 전역 예외 처리 (@ControllerAdvice)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [Lab02-1] 존재하지 않는 학생 → 커스텀 404
###  GlobalExceptionHandler 적용 전: Spring 기본 500 흰 화면
###  적용 후: error/404.html 커스텀 페이지 (EntityNotFoundException)
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/99999
Accept: text/html

> {%
// 404.html이 정상 렌더링되면 status 200 (View 응답)
client.test("응답 도달", () =>
    client.assert([200, 404, 500].includes(response.status)));
// 적용 후 검증
client.test("커스텀 404 메시지 포함", () =>
    client.assert(response.body.includes("찾을 수 없") ||
                  response.body.includes("404")));
%}

###

### [Lab02-2] API 단건 — 존재하지 않는 ID
###  StudentApiController가 RuntimeException 던짐 → 500
###  (REST는 별도 @ExceptionHandler로 JSON 응답 권장 — 본 lab은 MVC 위주)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students/99999
Accept: application/json

> {%
client.test("응답 도달", () =>
    client.assert([200, 404, 500].includes(response.status)));
%}

###

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Lab 03 — Bean Validation (StudentForm 검증)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [Lab03-1] 빈 이름 → @NotBlank 실패 → 폼 재렌더링 (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=&studentId=202300999&email=test@test.com

> {%
client.test("검증 실패 → 폼 재렌더링 (200)", () =>
    client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("name 에러 메시지", () =>
    client.assert(response.body.includes("이름") &&
                  (response.body.includes("필수") || response.body.includes("error"))));
%}

###

### [Lab03-2] 학번 8자리 → @Pattern 실패
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=홍길동테스트&studentId=20230099&email=test@test.com

> {%
client.test("Pattern 검증 실패 → 폼 재렌더링", () =>
    client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("학번 에러 메시지", () =>
    client.assert(response.body.includes("9자리") ||
                  response.body.includes("학번")));
%}

###

### [Lab03-3] 잘못된 이메일 → @Email 실패
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=홍길동테스트&studentId=202300888&email=not-an-email

> {%
client.test("Email 검증 실패", () =>
    client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("이메일 에러 메시지", () =>
    client.assert(response.body.includes("이메일") ||
                  response.body.includes("형식")));
%}

###

